WEBVTT

00:00:30.063 --> 00:00:31.063
RED ARMILLARY SASH

00:01:18.938 --> 00:01:20.271
AGENT FROM ABOVE

00:01:20.896 --> 00:01:25.271
KARMA

00:01:30.980 --> 00:01:33.896
You're Ho Chun-lai's ghosts, aren't you?

00:01:36.355 --> 00:01:38.396
Excuse me. Does it hurt?

00:01:40.146 --> 00:01:41.938
Let me introduce myself.

00:01:42.021 --> 00:01:44.771
My name's Hsiao-ming. I'm a ghost too.

00:01:45.230 --> 00:01:47.730
When I was alive,
I was into anime and gaming.

00:01:51.438 --> 00:01:54.980
You've been put under a spell.
I can lift it and set you free.

00:01:55.980 --> 00:01:59.438
But first you must tell me
what Ho Chun-lai is up to.

00:02:01.188 --> 00:02:03.563
His Majesty threatened Uncle Chen--

00:02:05.646 --> 00:02:08.188
When His Majesty arrives,
he'll devour you.

00:02:08.688 --> 00:02:11.146
He'll rip out your heart and eat it!

00:02:13.938 --> 00:02:16.480
His Majesty, you mean the Demon King?

00:02:16.563 --> 00:02:17.896
Your uncle is Chen Chi-sha?

00:02:19.813 --> 00:02:22.480
Rip out your heart and eat it!

00:02:46.480 --> 00:02:47.688
The spell is lifted.

00:02:50.771 --> 00:02:52.313
Don't let me see you again.

00:03:01.438 --> 00:03:02.313
They left?

00:03:03.188 --> 00:03:05.063
Didn't you want to pursue them? Go on.

00:03:05.813 --> 00:03:07.605
They're ghosts. They scare me.

00:03:08.105 --> 00:03:10.688
-You're a ghost too.
-But not like that.

00:03:10.771 --> 00:03:14.396
They're not right in the head.
I should keep my options open.

00:03:14.480 --> 00:03:17.438
DONGFENG MARKET

00:03:17.521 --> 00:03:19.688
Rarely do true friends meet at all

00:03:20.563 --> 00:03:22.105
Like rising stars as others fall

00:03:22.188 --> 00:03:24.605
-I'm back.
-Hey, long night?

00:03:30.063 --> 00:03:30.938
Chieh.

00:03:31.688 --> 00:03:33.105
Why'd you bring that back?

00:03:36.563 --> 00:03:37.688
You can see me?

00:03:39.188 --> 00:03:42.396
They've all had their third eye opened.
Everyone can see you.

00:03:42.896 --> 00:03:43.855
So behave yourself.

00:03:44.688 --> 00:03:46.188
-Oh.
-Hey, old guard.

00:03:46.771 --> 00:03:48.438
-I'll leave him with you.
-Sure.

00:03:48.521 --> 00:03:49.771
Hello.

00:03:49.855 --> 00:03:51.063
-You're new here?
-Yes.

00:03:51.146 --> 00:03:53.230
I'll show you around the place later.

00:03:53.313 --> 00:03:56.146
Okay. So, do you have the internet here?

00:03:56.230 --> 00:03:57.855
Yes. Fiber optic.

00:04:05.938 --> 00:04:06.771
Why're you here?

00:04:13.438 --> 00:04:15.105
It's almost 11, get inside.

00:04:17.646 --> 00:04:18.646
Han Chieh.

00:04:19.355 --> 00:04:21.521
I talked to my dad earlier.

00:04:25.188 --> 00:04:27.480
He cried and asked me to forgive him.

00:04:28.063 --> 00:04:30.938
He said they stopped loving each other
a long time ago.

00:04:31.021 --> 00:04:33.230
They're planning on getting a divorce.

00:04:41.188 --> 00:04:42.021
Han Chieh.

00:04:43.063 --> 00:04:44.230
What's wrong?

00:04:44.813 --> 00:04:45.688
Stay back.

00:05:09.521 --> 00:05:10.355
FENGYUAN TEMPLE

00:05:12.438 --> 00:05:13.396
Dad!

00:05:14.396 --> 00:05:15.605
Mom!

00:05:39.980 --> 00:05:41.480
Just give me a break.

00:05:57.605 --> 00:05:59.105
Can't help yourself, can you?

00:06:02.230 --> 00:06:03.105
What do you want?

00:06:08.188 --> 00:06:12.021
I've come to give you some good news.

00:06:14.063 --> 00:06:15.771
I shouldn't be telling you this.

00:06:19.105 --> 00:06:20.521
The winning lotto numbers?

00:06:29.771 --> 00:06:31.730
That girl you care about

00:06:33.188 --> 00:06:34.605
is being reincarnated today.

00:06:39.146 --> 00:06:41.063
Don't say I never help you out.

00:06:46.188 --> 00:06:48.646
You were there for her
in her darkest hour.

00:06:49.313 --> 00:06:50.938
She died in peace.

00:06:51.896 --> 00:06:55.188
It's time to let her go.

00:07:02.063 --> 00:07:03.146
Promise me.

00:07:05.063 --> 00:07:06.605
After I die,

00:07:07.438 --> 00:07:09.605
carry on with your life, okay?

00:07:10.605 --> 00:07:11.605
Don't worry.

00:07:13.063 --> 00:07:14.813
When you're reborn, I'll find you.

00:07:18.355 --> 00:07:20.271
How could you possibly find me?

00:07:20.813 --> 00:07:23.521
I won't remember you,
and you won't recognize me.

00:07:24.021 --> 00:07:25.355
I'll know it's you.

00:07:49.188 --> 00:07:50.605
Why the sudden nice gesture?

00:07:53.271 --> 00:07:55.396
Consider it a personal favor.

00:07:55.480 --> 00:07:57.896
Don't let me down
with the rest of your tasks.

00:08:02.730 --> 00:08:04.063
Why are you still here?

00:08:04.813 --> 00:08:06.146
Han Chieh, you're awake?

00:08:30.313 --> 00:08:33.480
I told my mom I'd be out
all night filming with the crew.

00:08:40.105 --> 00:08:43.271
Han Chieh,
what happened to you last night?

00:08:48.730 --> 00:08:50.855
It's a side effect of using the milk caps.

00:08:50.938 --> 00:08:52.980
You work hard for the Third Crown Prince.

00:08:53.063 --> 00:08:55.396
Why would there be side effects?

00:08:56.313 --> 00:08:58.438
He kept me alive
to be his agent from above

00:08:59.021 --> 00:09:01.146
so I could atone for my sins.

00:09:01.896 --> 00:09:05.771
He needs to keep a tight rein on me,
or he could lose face.

00:09:13.396 --> 00:09:14.438
All right.

00:09:15.438 --> 00:09:16.813
Where's that lousy geek?

00:09:20.855 --> 00:09:21.688
Hi.

00:09:21.771 --> 00:09:23.605
Did you sleep well last night?

00:09:24.563 --> 00:09:25.813
Fuck.

00:09:29.688 --> 00:09:30.855
Can't you knock first?

00:09:32.688 --> 00:09:36.396
It's not a bad setup,
but the soundproofing isn't great.

00:09:37.105 --> 00:09:39.813
All of these houses have dark histories.

00:09:40.396 --> 00:09:43.271
The feng shui here
is just perfect for ghosts.

00:09:43.355 --> 00:09:45.688
I could put my computer desk here…

00:09:47.438 --> 00:09:49.813
Then my bed… one step, two steps…

00:09:52.230 --> 00:09:55.313
I'll burn all this stuff for you
when I have time.

00:09:55.896 --> 00:09:57.230
Thank you.

00:09:57.313 --> 00:10:00.605
But I don't want anything too old
or a mattress that's too soft.

00:10:00.688 --> 00:10:02.855
Oh, never mind. I'll message you later.

00:10:03.813 --> 00:10:04.813
I asked my mom.

00:10:04.896 --> 00:10:07.730
She did pay that feng shui master
to save her marriage.

00:10:07.813 --> 00:10:11.355
But she didn't know he'd cause any harm.
She won't contact him again.

00:10:11.438 --> 00:10:12.938
But how did she find him?

00:10:13.521 --> 00:10:15.646
She said a friend introduced them.

00:10:15.730 --> 00:10:18.938
They always met at a cafe
and she doesn't know his real name.

00:10:21.855 --> 00:10:26.105
Chieh brings lost ghosts
like you back here from time to time.

00:10:26.188 --> 00:10:27.980
Some only stay for a bit.

00:10:28.063 --> 00:10:31.771
Some stay and like it here.
Then they never leave.

00:10:31.855 --> 00:10:33.896
I see. What about lady ghosts?

00:10:35.771 --> 00:10:36.688
Behave yourself.

00:10:38.605 --> 00:10:40.855
Han Chieh, what are your plans for him?

00:10:43.313 --> 00:10:45.980
He has nowhere to go
and there are plenty of rooms here.

00:10:46.063 --> 00:10:47.688
He can take his pick.

00:10:48.396 --> 00:10:50.230
Lots of lady ghosts live here too.

00:10:50.313 --> 00:10:52.230
If he behaves, I'll set him up with one.

00:10:53.855 --> 00:10:56.646
I thought you
were going to beat him out of existence.

00:10:56.730 --> 00:10:59.105
He's an idiot, but he's not evil.

00:11:00.021 --> 00:11:01.563
I wasn't told to kill all ghosts.

00:11:02.146 --> 00:11:03.438
That's not my thing.

00:11:04.730 --> 00:11:05.563
Let's go.

00:11:12.021 --> 00:11:14.521
Han Chieh, what's your task today?

00:11:14.605 --> 00:11:16.021
What kind of ghost is it?

00:11:18.896 --> 00:11:20.771
God knows why I let you tag along.

00:11:21.605 --> 00:11:23.063
Because you're a good guy.

00:11:23.146 --> 00:11:25.271
You can't bear the thought
of me dying alone.

00:11:25.355 --> 00:11:27.813
So you let me have some fun,
even if I'm a drag.

00:11:28.313 --> 00:11:29.813
Quit going on about death.

00:11:29.896 --> 00:11:31.771
Also, we're not here to have fun.

00:11:33.271 --> 00:11:34.230
Got it.

00:11:44.355 --> 00:11:45.188
Well done.

00:11:45.271 --> 00:11:47.480
Time to go home. Was that fun?

00:11:51.355 --> 00:11:53.063
I opened their third eyes for now.

00:11:53.146 --> 00:11:56.646
Tonight, I need to take care
of two ghosts that are bothering them.

00:11:57.188 --> 00:12:01.021
These two ghosts are completely obsessed.
It'll take some doing.

00:12:32.730 --> 00:12:33.563
Son.

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:37.480
You hired another master to deal with us?

00:12:37.563 --> 00:12:39.813
Look, we really need to talk.

00:12:39.896 --> 00:12:43.980
These two women were childless,
so they treated their nephew like a son.

00:12:44.063 --> 00:12:48.313
He then let them
be like grandmothers to his own son Chih.

00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:51.980
You should study Chinese. Forget English.

00:12:52.063 --> 00:12:55.271
They couldn't part with Chih,
so stayed here after they died.

00:12:55.355 --> 00:12:59.771
Soon, they became too overbearing
and things got out of hand.

00:12:59.855 --> 00:13:01.771
They'd appear in the parents' dreams

00:13:01.855 --> 00:13:03.646
with new instructions each night.

00:13:03.730 --> 00:13:06.021
But the two ladies often disagreed

00:13:06.521 --> 00:13:08.980
and would even argue
in the middle of the night.

00:13:09.063 --> 00:13:10.730
The family have had enough.

00:13:10.813 --> 00:13:13.188
The foot of the bed
shouldn't face the door.

00:13:13.271 --> 00:13:14.480
Did you help him study?

00:13:14.563 --> 00:13:16.313
Why haven't you moved it?

00:13:16.396 --> 00:13:17.521
Ladies.

00:13:20.313 --> 00:13:22.438
You always disagree.
Who should he listen to?

00:13:22.521 --> 00:13:24.105
Me, of course. I'm the eldest.

00:13:24.188 --> 00:13:27.063
Nope. I majored in education.
He should listen to me.

00:13:29.563 --> 00:13:31.188
He should listen to his parents.

00:13:31.271 --> 00:13:34.896
Nonsense. We always
listened to our grandparents.

00:13:34.980 --> 00:13:37.188
Right, they know best.

00:13:37.271 --> 00:13:39.605
Young couples
have their own ideas on parenting.

00:13:39.688 --> 00:13:43.021
How's the kid supposed to sleep?
How's he ever gonna grow up?

00:13:43.105 --> 00:13:45.855
Ghosts shorten a human's lifespan
if they get too close.

00:13:45.938 --> 00:13:49.355
I majored in science.
No one believes those ghost stories.

00:13:49.438 --> 00:13:50.480
-Sis.
-Yes?

00:13:50.563 --> 00:13:52.188
-We're literally ghosts now.
-Oh.

00:13:53.563 --> 00:13:54.688
Then…

00:13:54.771 --> 00:13:58.521
If a ghost gets anywhere near Chih,
I'll chase it off.

00:13:59.021 --> 00:14:02.230
Actually, I understand how you feel.

00:14:02.855 --> 00:14:03.980
And who are you?

00:14:04.438 --> 00:14:05.605
Do you have kids?

00:14:05.688 --> 00:14:08.980
-Adults are speaking, keep quiet.
-Such poor manners.

00:14:09.063 --> 00:14:11.980
Bet she's the type
who doesn't give up her seat on the bus.

00:14:12.063 --> 00:14:13.896
-Right.
-Shocking manners.

00:14:16.980 --> 00:14:19.938
Listen, I'm really thankful to you both.

00:14:26.980 --> 00:14:29.230
But this just can't go on.

00:14:30.813 --> 00:14:34.646
Feng is pregnant with our second child,
and Chih will start school soon.

00:14:35.438 --> 00:14:38.521
We just want to live ordinary lives.

00:14:46.521 --> 00:14:50.146
Thank you for your kindness,
but we just can't take it anymore.

00:14:53.605 --> 00:14:55.271
Chih won…

00:15:00.105 --> 00:15:01.730
You reek! Come here.

00:15:01.813 --> 00:15:02.688
All right…

00:15:04.980 --> 00:15:05.855
Big hug.

00:15:09.813 --> 00:15:11.355
Please leave us be.

00:15:44.396 --> 00:15:45.355
Han Chieh.

00:15:45.855 --> 00:15:47.980
-Is that done now?
-Stay close.

00:15:57.188 --> 00:15:59.313
This is what you get for meddling.

00:16:00.188 --> 00:16:01.021
Let's go.

00:16:02.355 --> 00:16:07.021
We have nowhere to go now because of you!

00:16:08.355 --> 00:16:10.021
Where you gonna run to now?

00:16:30.438 --> 00:16:33.230
Han Chieh, weren't we just here?

00:16:35.980 --> 00:16:38.021
Fuck, we're going around in circles.

00:16:59.813 --> 00:17:02.563
You heartless monsters!
You've torn our family apart.

00:17:02.646 --> 00:17:04.855
Who'll take care of Chih with us gone?

00:17:04.938 --> 00:17:06.063
You're long gone.

00:17:06.980 --> 00:17:08.063
Don't listen to him!

00:17:08.146 --> 00:17:10.688
-Let's break his legs!
-Teach him a lesson!

00:17:11.896 --> 00:17:12.813
GOLDEN BRICK

00:17:30.980 --> 00:17:34.396
You already turned our son against us.
Now you want to kill us!

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:37.688
Do you even know
what respecting your elders means?

00:17:38.188 --> 00:17:41.271
Humans must live by laws
and so must ghosts.

00:17:41.938 --> 00:17:44.896
Even as ghosts,
you have to follow the rules.

00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:47.396
No one ever taught us how to be ghosts.

00:17:47.480 --> 00:17:50.688
That's why my boss
asked me to talk to you.

00:17:50.771 --> 00:17:52.730
But if I can't get through to you…

00:17:55.313 --> 00:17:57.063
you might never see the kid again.

00:18:00.688 --> 00:18:04.230
I died with so much left undone.
It's just not fair!

00:18:04.313 --> 00:18:06.313
Life is so cruel.

00:18:07.688 --> 00:18:08.813
Ladies,

00:18:08.896 --> 00:18:12.688
they say that a person's consciousness
pauses the moment they die.

00:18:12.771 --> 00:18:15.105
Perhaps that's why you haven't realized

00:18:15.188 --> 00:18:17.771
that what you're doing
is actually hurting Chih.

00:18:22.896 --> 00:18:23.855
Ladies.

00:18:24.730 --> 00:18:28.396
It's hard to find peace in death
if you fixate on the physical world.

00:18:29.063 --> 00:18:30.688
It's time to let go.

00:18:30.771 --> 00:18:34.646
Easy for you to say now. But you'll change
your tune when you're our age.

00:18:34.730 --> 00:18:36.146
Let go?

00:18:36.230 --> 00:18:38.771
Can you let go of the one you love?

00:18:46.396 --> 00:18:47.521
Ladies.

00:18:47.605 --> 00:18:51.021
If you want a son or grandson,
just find someone else.

00:18:51.105 --> 00:18:52.563
You can care for him instead.

00:18:53.605 --> 00:18:55.230
Think we can just replace him?

00:18:55.313 --> 00:18:56.938
It's not like adopting a stray.

00:18:57.021 --> 00:18:58.896
Where can we find a new grandson?

00:18:58.980 --> 00:19:02.355
I know this guy.
He's 30, but still acts like a child.

00:19:02.438 --> 00:19:05.563
-And he's not afraid of ghosts.
-You know someone like that?

00:19:11.813 --> 00:19:14.980
Han Chieh, I'm not sure
we're on the same page here…

00:19:15.855 --> 00:19:18.980
Why does he look like that?
He looks weird.

00:19:19.688 --> 00:19:23.021
Mr. Han, didn't you say
there were lots of kids here?

00:19:23.105 --> 00:19:25.105
Why've you taken us to see this weirdo?

00:19:26.271 --> 00:19:28.313
He's not that bad. You can be friends.

00:19:28.396 --> 00:19:31.355
Get to know your neighbors.
There are lots of kids about.

00:19:32.146 --> 00:19:33.771
You're so full of it.

00:19:33.855 --> 00:19:37.105
If it wasn't for him up above,
I wouldn't give you the time of day.

00:19:38.105 --> 00:19:39.688
This place is a pigsty.

00:19:39.771 --> 00:19:41.605
It's just asking for trouble.

00:19:41.688 --> 00:19:42.813
What's going on?

00:19:43.855 --> 00:19:46.021
Do me a favor. Be a good grandson.

00:19:46.105 --> 00:19:48.105
-It's filthy.
-Get on their good side.

00:19:48.188 --> 00:19:51.688
-At least we're still together…
-I'll buy you a new computer.

00:19:54.355 --> 00:19:55.355
You, over there.

00:20:02.438 --> 00:20:04.813
Turn around. What's your name?

00:20:05.896 --> 00:20:07.146
Hello, ladies.

00:20:07.230 --> 00:20:10.396
I'm Wang Hsiao-ming.
How can I be of service?

00:20:33.063 --> 00:20:35.605
Boss, that's Chen Chi-sha over there.

00:20:38.313 --> 00:20:39.855
Creepy old fraudster.

00:20:45.480 --> 00:20:46.355
Master Chen.

00:20:47.230 --> 00:20:50.230
About that incident
with the Chinghua and Wutung clans.

00:20:50.313 --> 00:20:52.938
Whenever you're involved,
lots of people end up dead.

00:20:54.188 --> 00:20:57.813
Do you really think it's good
when the police get involved?

00:20:58.855 --> 00:20:59.980
Why wouldn't it be?

00:21:01.355 --> 00:21:05.188
Mr. Liu wants to inform you
that the next target is the Heilung Clan.

00:21:05.271 --> 00:21:07.355
He'd prefer it done quietly.

00:21:11.813 --> 00:21:13.480
Go tell Mr. Liu

00:21:13.563 --> 00:21:17.188
to come in person
next time he wants to talk to me.

00:21:21.063 --> 00:21:22.230
Boss, are you okay?

00:21:23.396 --> 00:21:24.813
-Let's go.
-Come on.

00:21:25.313 --> 00:21:26.146
Hurry!

00:21:38.605 --> 00:21:40.355
WUMENG OCCULTIST COLLUDES WITH TRIADS

00:21:40.438 --> 00:21:42.313
WUMENG OCCULTIST REFINES HELLSPAWN

00:21:42.396 --> 00:21:44.271
DEMON KING ENTICES MAN

00:21:46.980 --> 00:21:49.688
His Majesty threatened Uncle Chen--

00:21:50.396 --> 00:21:53.605
His Majesty, you mean the Demon King?
Your uncle is Chen Chi-sha?

00:21:56.396 --> 00:21:59.813
DRUNKARD DIES AND SEEKS REVENGE

00:22:03.480 --> 00:22:06.021
I looked into Ho Chun-lai.
His background is fake.

00:22:07.230 --> 00:22:08.605
I've met Ho Chun-lai.

00:22:09.688 --> 00:22:10.896
It couldn't be him.

00:22:11.480 --> 00:22:14.021
Chen Chi-sha is probably
the one behind all this.

00:22:14.813 --> 00:22:17.688
Chen Chi-sha?
Didn't you say he was bad news?

00:22:18.355 --> 00:22:19.855
He is.

00:22:19.938 --> 00:22:22.980
But the real one to watch out for
is his boss, the Demon King.

00:22:24.230 --> 00:22:25.938
He runs things down in hell.

00:22:26.021 --> 00:22:30.188
Five years ago, he enticed Chen Chi-sha
into trying to summon him back.

00:22:47.355 --> 00:22:48.230
Demon King?

00:22:57.105 --> 00:22:58.813
What is Chen Chi-sha up to?

00:23:01.563 --> 00:23:05.521
Since the Third Crown Prince defeated him,
he's been sealed away in hell.

00:23:06.605 --> 00:23:10.563
If he wants to return to the Human Realm,
a human must help summon him,

00:23:11.063 --> 00:23:14.313
remove the seal and become his agent.

00:23:36.271 --> 00:23:38.021
The scent of the Human Realm.

00:23:39.271 --> 00:23:40.438
I've really missed it.

00:23:45.563 --> 00:23:48.855
Know your place, mortal.
Do you even realize who I am?

00:23:48.938 --> 00:23:50.896
The most insufferable maggot down there.

00:23:50.980 --> 00:23:53.021
Do me a favor and fuck off back to hell.

00:25:05.980 --> 00:25:10.605
If you dare get in my way,
I'll drag you down to hell with me.

00:25:40.938 --> 00:25:42.646
NINE DRAGONS DIVINE FIRE BARRIER

00:25:59.355 --> 00:26:01.021
You little punk.

00:26:01.105 --> 00:26:03.563
I won't forget you.

00:26:20.688 --> 00:26:22.771
You got lucky this time.

00:26:24.188 --> 00:26:28.355
But there will always be people
in this world

00:26:28.438 --> 00:26:30.771
willing to summon him
for their own selfish ends.

00:26:31.396 --> 00:26:33.230
-Next time--
-Won't be a next time.

00:26:41.396 --> 00:26:44.146
Chen Chi-sha promised me
he'd give up that life

00:26:44.688 --> 00:26:46.646
and never practice the dark arts again.

00:26:47.938 --> 00:26:50.313
But now he's secretly
stirring things up again.

00:26:53.021 --> 00:26:55.021
If the Demon King's planning a comeback,

00:26:55.105 --> 00:26:58.646
he'll probably give Chen Chi-sha
even more power this time.

00:27:16.438 --> 00:27:19.230
I'm retiring soon.
Are you trying to get me killed?

00:27:26.938 --> 00:27:28.855
Don't scare my bird.

00:27:29.938 --> 00:27:33.896
Whose fault is this? If you'd killed him,
none of this would've happened.

00:27:37.563 --> 00:27:41.146
I'm a Buddhist disciple.
Killing's not good for my karma.

00:27:43.438 --> 00:27:44.688
The Third Crown Prince?

00:27:46.438 --> 00:27:48.563
Your third eye is too weak to see him.

00:27:49.021 --> 00:27:50.313
-He's here?
-No.

00:27:51.105 --> 00:27:53.980
It's a psychic connection.
He can't appear in true form.

00:27:54.063 --> 00:27:56.021
You guys chat. I'll leave you to it.

00:27:56.105 --> 00:28:00.188
Wait up. I want to report my boss
for bullying at work.

00:28:00.271 --> 00:28:02.855
He makes me do overtime
with zero benefits.

00:28:02.938 --> 00:28:05.730
File a report with the Ministry of Labor,
not the police.

00:28:05.813 --> 00:28:08.313
I already sent Javvy to warn you.

00:28:08.396 --> 00:28:10.438
You're just too slow to get it.

00:28:11.646 --> 00:28:14.188
The Demon King
wants to enter the Human Realm again

00:28:14.271 --> 00:28:18.271
before your tasks are complete
and your successor takes over.

00:28:18.355 --> 00:28:20.480
So I'm leaving this in your hands.

00:28:20.563 --> 00:28:22.271
Shit. Can't you do it yourself?

00:28:22.355 --> 00:28:26.605
Kid, why bother recruiting you
if I have to do everything myself?

00:28:26.688 --> 00:28:29.188
Boss, just recruit someone else.

00:28:31.396 --> 00:28:32.271
Like this guy.

00:28:33.063 --> 00:28:35.938
He's a competent policeman
who fights for justice.

00:28:36.021 --> 00:28:38.438
-The perfect candidate.
-No thanks, I'm good.

00:28:38.521 --> 00:28:40.855
He's not a fan of mine. He worships Guan.

00:28:43.980 --> 00:28:46.230
Come on, worship the Third Crown Prince.

00:28:46.313 --> 00:28:48.688
He's right here. Prove you're a devotee.

00:28:48.771 --> 00:28:50.980
Me? I worship Lord Guan at work.

00:28:51.063 --> 00:28:54.271
As well as Xuanwu, the God of Wealth,
the Earth God and Yue Lao.

00:28:54.355 --> 00:28:57.230
I even go on Mazu pilgrimages.
I'm devoted enough already.

00:28:57.313 --> 00:28:58.980
Cut the crap.

00:28:59.063 --> 00:29:02.438
Just get on with your task
and be done with it.

00:29:03.896 --> 00:29:05.855
And what if I don't?

00:29:06.438 --> 00:29:08.230
Afraid of losing? Or scared of dying?

00:29:09.271 --> 00:29:11.605
Neither. You just piss me off.

00:29:13.938 --> 00:29:14.771
That's better.

00:29:15.355 --> 00:29:18.396
That's my agent from above.
Naturally rebellious.

00:29:18.896 --> 00:29:22.188
Don't say I didn't warn you
when the shit hits the fan.

00:29:26.271 --> 00:29:29.063
WUMENG OCCULTIST REFINES HELLSPAWN

00:29:29.146 --> 00:29:32.396
DEMON KING ENTICES MAN

00:30:13.688 --> 00:30:15.730
You're back? Good work.

00:30:33.771 --> 00:30:34.605
Curses lifted?

00:30:38.521 --> 00:30:39.521
Was it Han Chieh?

00:30:41.396 --> 00:30:42.771
Calm down.

00:30:43.271 --> 00:30:44.438
Can't we talk it out--

00:30:44.521 --> 00:30:49.730
You used us to threaten our uncle.
Only your death will free him.

00:30:58.105 --> 00:30:59.688
I really envy Master Chen.

00:31:01.063 --> 00:31:03.646
Having two such beautiful
and loving relatives.

00:31:04.271 --> 00:31:05.396
He's so lucky.

00:31:07.355 --> 00:31:08.271
A word of advice.

00:31:09.230 --> 00:31:11.771
Humans shouldn't let emotions rule them.

00:31:12.938 --> 00:31:13.855
Nor should ghosts.

00:32:15.313 --> 00:32:18.188
You know what to do next, don't you?

00:32:53.355 --> 00:32:55.105
ASCENT TO HEAVEN

00:32:55.980 --> 00:32:57.771
Mr. Liu offers you this tea,

00:32:59.563 --> 00:33:00.813
as a parting gift.

00:33:00.896 --> 00:33:01.938
Fuck!

00:33:11.521 --> 00:33:13.146
Fuck! What the hell?

00:33:55.563 --> 00:33:56.813
Han Chieh took the bait.

00:33:57.313 --> 00:34:01.855
Chen Chi-sha only failed to summon me
last time because of him,

00:34:01.938 --> 00:34:04.271
the Third Crown Prince's agent from above.

00:34:05.813 --> 00:34:06.646
Rest assured.

00:34:07.855 --> 00:34:11.480
I'll do a better job than him.
You can count on me.

00:34:11.563 --> 00:34:13.855
If this plan works out,

00:34:13.938 --> 00:34:17.230
my demonic power will increase again.

00:34:18.271 --> 00:34:22.105
And you'll get everything you wanted.